sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User (Staff)
    participant UI as Login Window
    participant S as Auth Service
    participant API as API Controller
    participant DB as Database
    participant Sess as User Session

    U->>UI: Open App
    UI->>U: Display Login Form
    U->>UI: Enter Application Credentials
    UI->>S: LoginAsync(User, Pass)
    S->>API: POST /api/Auth/Login
    API->>DB: Query User(Username)
    DB-->>API: Return User Record
    
    alt User Not Found OR Wrong Pass
        API-->>S: 401 Unauthorized
        S-->>UI: Return Null
        UI-->>U: Show Error "Sai tên đăng nhập/mật khẩu"
    else Valid Credentials
        API->>API: Generate JWT Token
        API-->>S: 200 OK (Token, Role, FullName)
        S->>Sess: Save Token & User Info
        S-->>UI: Return LoginResponse
        UI->>UI: Close Login Window
        UI->>U: Open Main Window
    end
